<dl class="app"><dt class="app_name">LyX</dt><dd class="app_img"><img src="/uploads/apps_lyx.png" alt="LyX" /></dd><dd class="app_desc">LyX is a document processor that encourages an approach to writing based on the structure of your documents (WYSIWYM) and not simply their appearance (WYSIWYG).

LyX combines the power and flexibility of TeX/LaTeX with the ease of use of a graphical interface. This results in world-class support for creation of mathematical content (via a fully integrated equation editor) and structured documents like academic articles, theses, and books.

</dd><dd class="app_feat"><ul><li>What You See Is What You Mean editor (looks like any word processor).</li></ul>

