</dd><dd class="app_feat"><ul><li>Built-in pdf viewer with synctex support and continuous view mode.</li><li>Unicode support, spell checking.</li><li>Clean and modern interface with wizards to generate code.</li></ul>

</dd><dd class="app_link"><a href="http://www.xm1math.net/texmaker/" title="">http://www.xm1math.net/texmaker/</a></dd></dl>
